
'''Adlo korar''' zaun asa [[Povitr Pustok]]acho poilo bhag. Hem Hebrevanchem Povitr Pustokacher adharlelem asa. Hebrevanchem Povitr Pustok mhonnge Israelitanche khup pornneo dhormik boroupam. Povitr Pustokacho dusro bhag zaun asa [[Novo korar]].
 
Adlea korarant veg-vegleo pustokam asat jim veg-veglea lokamnim boroilelim asat. Povitr pustokache ''experts'' mantat ki Adlea Korarant [[Job achem Pustok|Jobachem pustok]] soglleavon adlem mhonn jem 1500BC-int boroilelem ani [[Malaki achem Pustok|Malakiachem]] soglleavon novem mhonn, jem 400BC-int boroilelem.
 
